ml.codeboy.engine

Class Sprite

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.codeboy.engine.Sprite
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GameObject, UIObject

    public class Sprite
extends java.lang.Object
    represents a Sprite that gets drawn on the games window sprites are one of the layers specified by the Layer enum
